dcterms:description: A dataset containing math word problems used for training models to solve complex multi-step mathematical reasoning tasks.
dcterms:title: GSM8K

dcterms:description: A dataset created from reasoning paths obtained through inference on the GSM8K train set, used for supervised fine-tuning.
dcterms:title: Dataset D

dcterms:description: A dataset extracted from Dataset D, containing reasoning paths used for creating the supervised fine-tuning dataset.
dcterms:title: Dataset Dsf t

dcterms:description: A dataset created from reasoning paths for preference dataset generation.
dcterms:title: Dataset Ddpo

dcterms:description: A dataset used for training the Parietal Lobe Model, containing code-form reasoning paths and answers.
dcterms:title: Dataset Q0

dcterms:description: A dataset containing reasoning paths obtained through multiple iterations for training the Parietal Lobe Model.
dcterms:title: Dataset Qi

dcterms:description: A dataset created for generating high-quality plans from problems using the Frontal Lobe Model.
dcterms:title: Dataset Psf t

dcterms:description: A dataset containing plans generated from the Frontal Lobe Model for further processing.
dcterms:title: Dataset P

dcterms:description: A dataset containing plans generated from the GSM8K train set for training purposes.
dcterms:title: Dataset P ′

dcterms:description: A dataset containing plans generated from the GSM8K train set for further processing.
dcterms:title: Dataset P ′′
